 godta dei, og eit sivilisert samfunn m\u00e5 finne siviliserte m\u00e5tar \u00e5 m\u00f8te dei p\u00e5. Eg l\u00f8yser rett nok ingen fattigdomsproblem i verda om eg blir rausare med myntane mine n\u00e5r eg passerer dei. Men kanskje burde eg likevel vere det \u2013 som eit medmenneske.", "ola.stugu@ntnu.no"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|innsyn"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "2e5bb4a1791f6a5fef798aa76d49d3292bcecde607f2c4065af18cfae1dc3fa0"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-03-13T07:41:21.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Eg m\u00e5 berre vedg\u00e5 det: Eg likar ikkje \u00e5 sj\u00e5 tiggarar p\u00e5 gata."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://static.polarismedia.no/skins/prod/publication/adressa/gfx/applefavicon.png"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/e220fdb96bad04a0ef81a215491f1674cfca98aa.jpg?58c64d21"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Tiggarplagen -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "e220fdb96bad04a0ef81a215491f1674cfca98aa"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "innsyn"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["framande", "tigge"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": "guds"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/innsyn"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://static.polarismedia.no/skins/prod/publication/adressa/gfx/applefavicon.png"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "value": "Tiggarplagen"}, {"field": "og-type", "value": "ar